org.sxb.kit.concurrent

  • org.sxb.kit.concurrentを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    org.sxb.core.scheduling.concurrent
    Scheduling convenience classes for the java.util.concurrent and javax.enterprise.concurrent packages, allowing to set up a ThreadPoolExecutor or ScheduledThreadPoolExecutor as a bean in a Spring context.
    org.sxb.core.task
    任务调度用
    org.sxb.core.task.support
    Support classes for Spring's TaskExecutor abstraction.
    org.sxb.kit.concurrent
    多线程安全类包 并发处理用 任务调度用

  • org.sxb.kit.concurrentにより使用されるorg.sxb.kit.concurrentのクラス 
    クラスと説明
    FailureCallback
    Defines the contract for failure callbacks that accept the result of a ListenableFuture.
    FutureAdapter
    Abstract class that adapts a Future parameterized over S into a Future parameterized over T.
    ListenableFuture
    Extends the Future interface with the capability to accept completion callbacks.
    ListenableFutureCallback
    Defines the contract for callbacks that accept the result of a ListenableFuture.
    SuccessCallback
    Defines the contract for success callbacks that accept the result of a ListenableFuture.
